      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、{user}さんに\nご相談したいことがあるのですが、よろしいですか",
      "startTime": 2.9856826626,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……めずらしいですね、mihoさんが俺に改まって",
      "startTime": 6.5866665523,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "別に大したことではありません\n今度私達が出演する、生放送のバラエティのことです",
      "startTime": 13.68163263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "ロケ地には、前日の午後に移動する予定でしたが……\n私だけ、早めにそちらに行かせてほしいんです",
      "startTime": 21.78163263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "他の仕事のスケジュールはこちらで調整します\n構いませんね？",
      "startTime": 28.3954396825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それは構いませんけど……\nなんでまた、いきなり？",
      "startTime": 32.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "当日は、海辺の特設セットで\nMCのアイドルグループと対決する予定ですが",
      "startTime": 37.1649660904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "砂浜はスタジオと勝手が違いますし\nましてや生放送で、何が起こるか分かりませんから",
      "startTime": 43.5982994238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "あらかじめ現場を見て、対策を練っておきたいんです",
      "startTime": 47.2974592368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……さすがmihoさん\nバラエティ番組でも、本気で勝ちにいくつもりですね",
      "startTime": 52.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました\nそういうことなら、俺も一緒に前乗りしますよ",
      "startTime": 58.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "貴方にわざわざ引率していただく必要はありません",
      "startTime": 61.3493410587,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "むしろ、franとkanaが羽目を外さないように\n見張っておいていただきたいのですが",
      "startTime": 67.9988665103,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それは、俺にもちょっと荷が重いですね……",
      "startTime": 70.3882976691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "……それに、貴方だって\n私と行動するなんて、まっぴらでしょう",
      "startTime": 76.8887305259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……そこまでは言いませんよ\nmihoさんに思うところがあるのは否定しませんが",
      "startTime": 82.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルの手助けをするのが俺の仕事ですから\nそこは信用してほしいなあ……と",
      "startTime": 89.3333307902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "……これ以上言っても無駄なのは分かりました\nでは、前日からよろしくお願いします",
      "startTime": 96.5512416837,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6364.055363399999,
          "startTime": 102.9152970471
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――生放送前日。海辺の特設スタジオ予定地",
      "startTime": 100.5819535413,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2535.953283300003,
          "startTime": 103.1179068246
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "い、いやあ～、海に来ましたねえ……\n天気もいいですし、海風も気持ちいい……ですねえ……",
      "startTime": 107.8999949138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "私達は仕事で海に来ているんですよ\n観光気分なら、ホテルでメールでも片付けていて下さい",
      "startTime": 117.2493972775,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみません！\nでも、対策と言っても、何を調べるつもりなんですか？",
      "startTime": 123.2666615804,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7586.007696500004,
          "startTime": 130.8526692769
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-mhk019.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね、まずは……",
      "startTime": 128.0246167656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "気象庁のサイトによれば、明日の予想気温は……\n風速がこれで、風向きの予測は……",
      "startTime": 136.5960000671,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "ライブバトルがあるとすれば……\n波の音、環境音の影響もあるだろうし……",
      "startTime": 142.06267182,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "あの、明日の番組はあくまでバラエティで\nライブバトルをやる予定はないですよ",
      "startTime": 148.9666615804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "あらゆる事態を想定すると言ったでしょう\n何事も、準備しておくに越したことはありません",
      "startTime": 154.732014465,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7099.997456900013,
          "startTime": 161.8320119219
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-mhk016.m4a",
      "text": "音響機材のリストは後でスタッフにもらうとして\nさて、次は……",
      "startTime": 161.2367759008,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ちょっと、mihoさん？",
      "startTime": 162.7374015009,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_drag-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3929.253975999984,
          "startTime": 166.6666554769
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "あの、mihoさん……\nなんでいきなり、砂を掘ってるんですか……？",
      "startTime": 168.7666554769,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-mhk017.m4a",
      "text": "明日、kanaがサッカーで対決する予定ですから\n砂浜がどれくらい走りやすい状態なのかは重要です",
      "startTime": 175.7676322297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-mhk018.m4a",
      "text": "……結構、砂がさらさらしているわね\n撮影の時間帯は、確か引き潮……",
      "startTime": 182.8166281875,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cooking-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 179.5669521167
        }
